live1.blogspot.com/2013/01/chat-with-roshan-ravindra.html | title=I do not want to be the popular actor | publisher=gossiplankalive1| accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| TBD || ''[[Thanapathilage Gedara]]'' ||  || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/2018/07/11/?fn=sa18071125 |title=Film Thaanapathilage Gedara |publisher=Sarasaviya |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and accolades==\nHe has won several awards at the local stage drama festivals and television festivals for many dramatic roles.<ref name=bestactor /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/111127/Magazine/sundaytimestvtimes_4.html |title=\u2018Thaksalawa\u2019 tops Sumathi awards |publisher=Sunday Times |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n===Saasaviya Awards===\n{{Awards table}}\n|-\n|| 2017 ||| ''Nimnayaka Hudekalawa'' || [[34th Sarasaviya Awards|Best Supporting Actor]] || {{won}}\n|}\n\n===Presidential Awards===\n{{Awards table}}\n|-\n|| 2004 ||| ''Adaraneeya Wassanaya'' || Best Upcoming Actor || {{won}}\n|}\n\n===Sumathi Awards===\n{{Awards table}}\n|-\n|| 2006 ||| ''Idorayaka Mal Pipila'' || [[Sumathi Best Upcoming Teledrama Actor Award|Best Actor]] || {{won}}\n|-\n||  ||| ''Ahasin Watuna'' || Best Actor || {{nominated}}\n|-\n|| 2011 ||| ''Abarthu Atha''<ref>{{cite web|title=\u2018Thaksalawa\u2019 tops Sumathi awards|url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/111127/Magazine/sundaytimestvtimes_4.html|publisher=The Sunday Times}}</ref> || Best Actor || {{won}}\n|-\n|| 2012 ||| ''Mage Kaviya Mata Denna''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.gossiplankanews.com/2012/11/lux-sumathi-tele-awards-2012-nominations.html?m=1 |title=Nominations of Lux Sumathi Tele Awards 2012 |publisher=gossiplankanews |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref> || Best Supporting Actor || {{nominated}}\n|-\n|| 2015 ||| ''Jeewithayaka Kedapathak'' || Best Single Episode || {{won}}\n{{End}}\n\n===Raigam Tele'es===\n{{Awards table}}\n|-\n|| 2011 ||| ''Abarthu Atha''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lankadesha.com/raigam-tele-es-2010/ |title=Raigam Tele\u2019es 2010 Main award winners |publisher=lankadesha |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref> || Best Actor || {{won}}\n|-\n|| 2013 ||| || Best Actor || {{nominated}}\n|-\n|| 2016 ||| ''[[Daskon (TV series)|Daskon]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=Raigam Tele'es 2015 award winners|url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/2016/06/09/?fn=sa16060915|publisher=Sarasaviya}}</ref> || Best Actor || {{won}}\n|-\n|| 2018 ||| ''Sahodaraya''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundayobserver.lk/2019/03/31/arts/raigam-tele-awards-2018 |title=Raigam Tele Awards 2018 |publisher=Sunday Observer |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref> || Best Actor || {{won}}\n{{End}}\n\n===State Television Awards===\n{{Awards table}}\n|-\n|| 2015 ||| ''Daskon''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://srilankamirror.com/news/610-roshan-himali-win-state-television-awards |title=Roshan, Himali win state television awards |publisher=Sri Lanka Mirror |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref> || Best Actor || {{won}}\n{{End}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|nm6229748}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n{{Sinhala Cinema|state=collapsed}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ravindra, Roshan}}\n[[Category:Sri Lankan male film actors]]\n[[Category:Sinhalese male actors]]\n[[Category:Sri Lankan male television actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox person\n| name = Roshan Ravindra <br> \u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dc2\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\n| image = \n| caption = \n| nationality = [[Sri Lanka]]n\n| birth_date = \n| birth_name = Roshan Ravindra Rajapakse\n| spouse = Sanjeewani \n| children = 3\n| occupation = Actor, Producer\n| years_active = 2004\u2013present\n}}\n'''Roshan Ravindra Rajapakse''' (Sinhala: '''\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dc2\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb''') is an [[actor]] in [[Cinema of Sri Lanka|Sri Lankan cinema]], theater and television.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nfc.gov.lk/artist/roshan-ravindra-212/ | title=Roshan Ravindra | publisher=National Film Corporation Of Sri Lanka| accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://movietimes.lk/celebrity/\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dc2\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb/ | title=Actor Roshan Ravindra | publisher=movietimes | accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref> Highly versatile actor particularly act in dramatic roles, Ravindra is a recipeint of Best Actor Award in many local award festivals.<ref name= bestactor>{{cite web|last1=Thilakasiri|first1=Sameera|title=16th Sumathi Awards 2011|url=http://www.sandeshaya.org/16th-sumathi-awards-2011/|website=Sandeshaya dedicated to Sri Lankan Sinhala films, movies, cinema...|date=22 November 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Nominations for Raigam Tele\u2019es  {{!}} The Sundaytimes Sri Lanka|url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/130512/magazine/nominations-for-raigam-telees-43894.html|work=www.sundaytimes.lk}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nRavindra is married to Sanjeewani, and they have a son Nethruu and daughter Kethaki.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/2013/01/10/?fn=sa13011010|title=Chat with Roshan|publisher=Sarasaviya |accessdate=17 November 2017}}</ref> He is a disciple of Sri Lankan actor [[Mahendra Perera]].<ref>{{cite news|last1=lanka|first1=Gossip|title=Mahendra Perera likes to act with Sunny Leone|url=http://www.gossiplankahotnews.com/2014/06/mahendra-perera-likes-to-act-with-sunny.html|work=www.gossiplankahotnews.com}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nBefore acting, he worked as a make-up artist in some films such as ''Sudu Kalu Saha Alu''.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/061210/TV/002_10_12_2006.html | title=Sanath performs director's role | publisher=Sunday Times| accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref> His most popular television acting came through ''Uthuwan Kande Sura Saradiyal'' as title role,<ref>{{cite web | url=http://archives.sundayobserver.lk/2006/09/10/mag03.asp | title=Saradiel re-lived | publisher=Sunday Observer | accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref> and then in ''Sahodaraya''.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.asianmirror.lk/entertainment/item/25878-namal-jayasinghe-s-sahodaraya-from-november | title=Namal Jayasinghe's 'Sahodaraya' From November | publisher=Asian Mirror| accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref>  His first project as a television producer was the teledrama ''Rasthiyadukaraya'' Directed by Lakmini Amaradewa,<ref>{{cite news|title=Roshan ravindra, Roshan ravindra in sri lanka|url=http://www.gossip7.info/hot_lanka/show.php?id=3080#.WJM_TdJ94dU|work=www.gossip7.info}}</ref> followed by ''Kadadora'' directed by Rajiv Ananda.<ref>{{cite news|title=roshan ravindra, Roshan Ravindra in sri lanka|url=http://www.sithma.com/hot_lanka/show.php?id=2823#.WDGkz9J94dU|work=www.sithma.com}}</ref>\n\nIn 2020 he directed his maiden television serial ''Thanamalvila Kollek''.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dinamina.lk/2020/02/18/\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dda\u0dc2\u0dcf\u0d82\u0d9c/90477/\u0db8\u0dda-\u0db8\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dad-\u0d85\u0db7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2p | title=This moment is challenging | publisher=Dinamina | accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Selected television serials===\n{{Div col|colwidth=25em}}\n* ''Aebarthu Aetha'' '\n* ''Ahasin Watuna''  \n* ''Amuthu Minissu''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/120205/Magazine/sundaytimestvtimes_6.html |title=\u2018Amuthu Minissu\u2019 to appear soon |publisher=Sunday Times |accessdate=12 July 2018}}</ref>\n* ''Badde Kulawamiya''\n* ''Binari'' \n* ''[[Daskon (TV series)|Daskon]]''\n* ''Dedunnen Eha''<ref>{{cite web | url=http://archives.dailynews.lk/2010/06/23/art19.asp | title=Venturing 'beyond the rainbow' | publisher=Daily News | accessdate=30 July 2019}}</ref>\n* ''Degammediyawa'' \n* ''Fantasy Avenue''\n* ''Golu Thaththa''<ref>{{cite news|title=Golu Thaththa Teledrama On Location|url=http://www.gossiplankanews.com/2015/08/golu-thaththa-teledrama-on-l